name: Cosmic Highway Wii U
blurb: Cosmic Highway takes music and racing to a whole new level. Do you love engaging music, stunning visuals, and racing? We thought so.

rewards.reward: DIGITAL ACCESS-Get added to our upcoming developer mailing list. Also, receive one free song from the game. This mailing list is different than the one on our website currently. We will also create a special KickStarter Forum on our site for you all to interact with us and each other. The song will be in FLAC, AIF, and MP3.

DIGITAL SUPPORT-We will be putting your name in the KickStarter Supporter section of the credits on the game, we will also add you to the mailing list, give you access to the forum and give you the free song. (What a steal of a deal!)

DIGITAL MUSIC-Get a digital download of the Cosmic Highway Soundtrack. We are releasing 6 different soundtracks, 5 Digital and 1 Physical Soundtrack. We will be sending you a questionnaire asking which of the soundtracks you want. (Choose wisely)

The choices for the digital soundtrack are: 
The Scientist Edition (Rock/Electronic)
The Dark One Edition (Orchestral)
The Glitcher Edition (8Bit/Chiptunes)
The Inventor Edition (Classical/Victorian)
The Comic Edition (Jazz)

You also will get the previous rewards.

DIGITAL ART BOOK- Get a copy of the Maestro Interactive Games Digital Art Book. It will feature Cosmic Highway, Alien Drop, Alien Revenge, Alien Labyrinth, Fade Into Darkness, Percy Penguin's World, Maestro Mini Golf and more. (We will try to get as much content in it as possible for you) \r\n\r\nYou will also get all of the lower levels.

BONUS DIGITAL-We are rewarding our backers of this level with a unique gift. Get exclusive access to the story of our next title Fade Into Darkness, months before the short story and game become available for sale. We will also create a unique Forum for the backers for this game, to discuss it with us.\r\n\r\nAlso you will get the lower tiers

THE GAME AT RELEASE-We are rewarding our backers of this level with a copy of Cosmic Highway Wii U the day it is released on the Nintendo eShop. Plus for those that have access to an iOS device, we will give you a copy of one of our previous iOS releases, Maestro Mini Golf to download. (If you do not have an iOS device, we can provide you a PC/Mac version) \r\n\r\nYou will also get the previous rewards.

PHYSICAL MUSIC- Limited to 100 People -We are providing the physical soundtrack at this donation level. This is the last of the 6 soundtracks for Cosmic Highway. This will be the only way to get this soundtrack, each album cover will be signed by the developers and will contain the special world music. We will also be giving you one of the digital soundtracks of your choice. You will get every reward in Tier 1 (See the reward section to the left). \r\n\r\n($10 extra for shipping for non-US)

THE GAME EARLY: Limited to 5 People - Get the game ahead of the rest. We will be giving you the game early (a week-2weeks) 

You will also get two digital soundtracks and the other rewards in Tier 1. 
(See the reward section to the left)

SIGNED POSTER: Limited to 50 People- We are rewarding our backers for this level, a limited print run poster of Cosmic Highway. This poster will also be signed by the developers. 
You will also get every reward in Tier 1. 
(See the reward section to the left)
(Picture is a very tentative idea of the poster, we will share the final poster before the end of the kickstarted)

($25 extra for shipping for non-US)

ALMOST HIGH SCORE-Limited to 10 People-We will add a song inspired by a game of your choice in the game. You will also receive credit in the game in the audio section. 

You will also receive the Physical Soundtrack from the Tier 2 rewards, as well as all of the rewards in Tier 1.
(See the reward section to the left)

($10 extra for shipping for non-US)

THE ASSOCIATE PRODUCER- Limited to 2 People-For $250, we are giving two donators the chance to become Associate Producers on a Nintendo Wii U eShop title. 

You will also get the Physical Soundtrack from Tier 2 and you will get all the rewards in Tier 1.
($10 extra for shipping for non-US)

THE PARTY-Limited to 5 People (10 guests total) Come by Maestro Interactive Games studio and have a fun night with some of the developers. We will hook up the Wii U and play Cosmic Highway, and much more. We will be recording the night as well to show off on our website and YouTube, if you all allow us to do so. Dinner will be included and you will also leave with tons of autographed gifts and prizes. You will also get the game at Launch obviously. 
You will also have a unique credit listed in the game as well. 

*Please be able to get to Austin on your own*
